    <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">Help and guidance</h1>

    <section id="section-api-standards">
      <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">API standards</h2>
      <p class="govuk-body">You will have received an email regarding the API Standards (also provided below). APIs let applications talk to each other and share data, they are essential to our technical process.</p>
      <p class="govuk-body">To be able to test API integration, API stubs will be circulated to you on the Help to Grow: Digital Vendor Portal. </p>
      <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">About</h3>
      <p class="govuk-body">Help to Grow: Digital provide a number of APIs for Vendors to engage with. Our APIs will align to <a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/gds-api-technical-and-data-standards" class="govuk-link" target="_blank">Government Digital Service</a> practices. Our APIs are partner based Web APIs using REST specification.</p>
      
      <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Use</h3>
      <p class="govuk-body">Our APIs are available to allow Vendors to interact with our services and are presented via an api.gov.uk address.</p>
      
      <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Access</h3>
      <p class="govuk-body">Connecting to the APIs will require you as an organisation to be registered within the Vendor portal and to have provided us with an IP address(es) to allow your systems to connect to us. We will whitelist the IP address and provide an API key for access.</p>
      
      <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Making requests</h3>
      <p class="govuk-body">When receiving your key, we will also provide our API documentation allowing you to make calls to the system. All access will be monitored for the duration of each session.</p>
        <p class="govuk-body">For further information see the Government Digital Service guidance on API Technical and Data Standards.</p>
      <p class="govuk-body">If you have any technical questions that are specific to the API or grant token redemption process, please contact: <a href="mailto:vendors.helptogrow@beis.co.uk" class="govuk-link">vendors.helptogrow@beis.co.uk</a></p>
    </section>
